00:09:54,034 --> 00:09:56,358
As soon as you are limited by a file size.

222
00:09:56,358 --> 00:09:56,438
Uh-oh.

223
00:09:56,438 --> 00:09:57,800
As soon as you're limited by a file size.

224
00:10:05,645 --> 00:10:08,865
It's a lose-lose situation of the resolution that you're giving each

225
00:10:08,865 --> 00:10:12,046
individual frame of that file size or your frame rate.

226
00:10:12,046 --> 00:10:15,527
