239
00:10:46,510 --> 00:10:49,353
if I didn't care too much about my texture memory,

240
00:10:49,353 --> 00:10:51,695
I could go up to 1024, I could go up to 2K, 4K, whatever.

241
00:10:51,695 --> 00:10:55,239
But then I'm burning through that texture memory.

242
00:10:55,239 --> 00:10:56,760
